---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/athena.css';
---

<Layout title="Project Athena | Winston Koh" description="My person AI architecture. Zero babysitting. The autonomous 'Second Brain' that makes engineering context durable." showAthenaWidget={false}>
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="athena-hero">
        <div class="athena-hero-content">
            <h1 class="athena-headline">4,000 Memories.<br><span class="text-gradient">Zero Babysitting.</span></h1>
            <p class="athena-subhead">The autonomous "Second Brain" that makes engineering context durable.</p>
            <p class="athena-micro">Local-first. Logged. Repeatable.</p>

            <!-- Terminal Preview -->
            <div class="athena-terminal">
                <p><span class="prompt">></span> <span class="output">/start</span></p>
                <p><span class="output">âœ… Core Identity loaded.</span></p>
                <p><span class="output">âœ… Project State synced. (4,203 nodes)</span></p>
                <p><span class="output">âœ… Semantic Memory primed.</span></p>
                <p><span class="output">ðŸŸ¢ SYSTEM READY.</span></p>
                <p><span class="prompt">></span> <span class="output">Waiting for command...</span><span
                        class="cursor"></span></p>
                <p class="timestamp">Last run: 2025-12-30 21:30 SGT</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Demo Embed (Show Don't Tell) -->
            <div class="demo-embed-container">
                <div class="video-container"
                    style="padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; height: 0; background: #0a0a0f;">
                    <iframe src="/assets/images/athena-demo-live.html"
                        style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none;"
                        title="Athena Terminal Demo">
                    </iframe>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="athena-cta-row">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://github.com/winstonkoh87/Athena-Public" target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener">View the Code â†’</a>
                <a href="#receipts" class="secondary-link">See what it does â†“</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
    <section class="athena-section">
        <h2>The Problem</h2>
        <p style="color: #ccd6f6; font-size: 1.1rem;">Codebases rot. Context gets lost. Same problems solved twice.
        </p>
        <ul class="pain-list">
            <li>Notes scattered across docs, chats, terminals, repos</li>
            <li>Same questions re-researched weekly</li>
            <li>No consistent memory + no consistent execution loop</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: #8892b0;">Athena is my attempt to make engineering context <strong
                style="color: #ccd6f6;">durable</strong>.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- THE RECEIPTS (PROOF) -->
    <section id="receipts" class="athena-section">
        <h2>The Receipts</h2>
        <p style="color: #8892b0;">Query in. Context out. Action logged.</p>

        <div class="proof-grid">
            <div class="proof-card">
                <div class="value metric-value">4,203</div>
                <div class="label">Vector Memories</div>
                <div class="meaning">Older decisions recalled without hunting</div>
            </div>
            <div class="proof-card">
                <div class="value metric-value">200</div>
                <div class="label">Protocols Indexed</div>
                <div class="meaning">Reusable playbooks for debugging, shipping, ops</div>
            </div>
            <div class="proof-card">
                <div class="value">~1.2s</div>
                <div class="label">Avg Query Time</div>
                <div class="meaning">Hybrid search: BM25 + semantic</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p style="color: #64ffda; margin-top: 1.5rem; display: flex; gap: 1.5rem;">
            <a href="https://github.com/winstonkoh87/Athena-Public" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                style="color: inherit;">Explore the codebase â†’</a>
            <a href="/articles/athena-public-launch" style="color: inherit;">Read the Launch Story â†’</a>
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- WHAT IT IS / ISN'T -->
    <section class="athena-section" style="padding-top: 0;">
        <div class="boundary-box">
            <h3>What Athena Is (and Isn't)</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Is:</strong> A personal RAG system for knowledge recall + agentic execution</li>
                <li><strong>Is:</strong> An operating system for my engineering workflow</li>
                <li><strong>Isn't:</strong> A chatbot or consumer product</li>
                <li><strong>Isn't:</strong> Magic â€” everything is logged, repeatable, auditable</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE LOOP (ARCHITECTURE) -->
    <section class="athena-section">
        <h2>The Loop</h2>
        <p style="color: #8892b0;">How data moves through Athena.</p>

        <div class="mermaid-container"
            style="background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.5); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); margin: 2rem 0;">
            <pre class="mermaid">
graph LR
A[Query] --> B[Hybrid Retrieval]
B --> C[Context Pack]
C --> D[LLM Reason]
D --> E[Execute]
E --> F[Log + Write-back]
F -.-> A
            </pre>
        </div>

        <div class="design-note">
            <h4>Why Hybrid Search?</h4>
            <p>Semantic alone misses keywords. BM25 alone misses intent. Hybrid (RRF) gives best recall.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="design-note" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
            <h4>Why Write-back Memory?</h4>
            <p>Every decision is quicksaved. Tomorrow's Athena knows what today's Athena decided.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- OPERATOR EVIDENCE -->
    <section class="athena-section">
        <h2>Operator Evidence</h2>
        <p style="color: #8892b0;">This isn't a demo. I use it daily.</p>

        <div class="operator-grid">
            <div class="operator-stat">
                <div class="num">17</div>
                <div class="desc">Sessions this month</div>
            </div>
            <div class="operator-stat">
                <div class="num">99.9%</div>
                <div class="desc">Uptime (local)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="operator-stat">
                <div class="num">~50</div>
                <div class="desc">Quicksaves/week</div>
            </div>
            <div class="operator-stat">
                <div class="num">0</div>
                <div class="desc">Data sent to cloud storage</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Day in the Life timeline -->
        <div class="athena-terminal" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <p class="timestamp">// Day in the life</p>
            <p><span class="prompt">09:12</span> <span class="output">/start sprint</span></p>
            <p><span class="prompt">10:47</span> <span class="output">/recall portfolio-v2.1-spec</span></p>
            <p><span class="prompt">14:03</span> <span class="output">/quicksave "Deployed Athena page
                    rebuild"</span></p>
            <p><span class="prompt">22:18</span> <span class="output">/end</span></p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="athena-cta-section">
        <h2>Want to build something like this?</h2>
        <p class="subtext">Internal AI systems. Ops automation. Knowledge engines.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://tally.so/r/3xjo1O" target="_blank">Initialize Project</a>
        <ul class="cta-bullets">
            <li>Best for teams with repeated research + SOPs</li>
            <li>Works with your docs + repos</li>
            <li>Can be local-first / private</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Mermaid.js -->
    <script type="module" is:inline>
        import mermaid from 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mermaid@10/dist/mermaid.esm.min.mjs';
        mermaid.initialize({
            startOnLoad: true,
            theme: 'dark',
            fontFamily: 'JetBrains Mono',
            themeVariables: {
                lineColor: '#64ffda',
                primaryColor: '#1a1a2e',
                primaryTextColor: '#ccd6f6',
                primaryBorderColor: '#64ffda',
                secondaryColor: '#0a0a0f',
                tertiaryColor: '#1a1a2e'
            }
        });
    </script>
</Layout>
